'''Brian Wesley Davis''' (born [[August 31]], [[1963]] in [[Phoenix, Arizona|Phoenix]], [[Arizona]]) is a former [[American football]] [[cornerback]] in the [[National Football League]] for the [[Washington Redskins]], the [[Seattle Seahawks]], the [[San Diego Chargers]], and the [[Minnesota Vikings]].  He played [[college football]] at the [[University of Nebraska]].

